<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.10">
<l>iruṭī kēca ṉempirā ṉilaṅkai yarakkarkula</l>
<l>muruṭu tīrtta pirāṉemmā ṉamararpemmā ṉeṉṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>teruṭi yāki ṉeñcē vaṇaṅkutiṇṇa maṟiyaṟintu</l>
<l>maruṭi yēlum viṭēlkaṇṭāy nampipaṟpa nāpaṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you understand, o heart, saying [and] saying “Riṣikeśa, our lord, lord</l>
<l>who ended the obstinacy of the Rakṣasa clan of Lankā, our lord, lord of the immortals”,</l>
<l>bow, know firmness. Knowing,</l>
<l>even if you are confused, don’t let go, see Nampi, the one with a lotus in his navel.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
